# Allow committed templates that follow the `.env.*.example` naming
# convention — the matching `.env.*` (without `.example`) holds the
# real secrets and stays ignored. See ADR-012 §5 for the dev-multisig
# pair (.env.dev-multisig.example committed, .env.dev-multisig hot).
!.env.*.example

